testcase.name: GIVEN multiple tags with some having prefix WHEN describe() THEN only tag with prefix is shown()
GIVEN no tag WHEN describe THEN describe is hash()
GIVEN annotated tag is present with merge commit WHEN describe() THEN annotated tag is chosen()
GIVEN with tag and no additional commit WHEN describe THEN describe is tag()
GIVEN with tag and additional commit WHEN describe() THEN count up by one()
GIVEN multiple tags on same commit WHEN describe() THEN annotated tag is chosen()
GIVEN tag set on deep commit WHEN describe() THEN return description()
GIVEN empty repository WHEN describe THEN describe is empty()
